  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- Hero -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="glow-1"></div>
  <div class="glow-2"></div>
  <div class="beta-pill"><div class="beta-dot"></div>Closed beta — invite codes available</div>
  <h1>Stop tracking.<br><em>Just talk to it.</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">One conversation replaces 10 health apps. Solas remembers everything about you and tells you what actually matters — without the logging, dashboards, or friction.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#waitlist" class="btn-primary">Request invite <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
    <a href="#how" class="btn-ghost">See how it works</a>
  </div>
  <p class="hero-note">iOS only · Free to start · No credit card</p>
</div>

<!-- Phone mockup -->
<div class="phone-wrap">
  <div class="phone">
    <div class="phone-notch"></div>
    <div class="phone-screen">
      <div class="msg-user"><span>Had 3 eggs and avocado for breakfast</span></div>
      <div class="msg-ai"><div class="ai-dot">S</div><span>Logged. 520 kcal, 32g protein, 18g fat, 4g carbs. Solid keto start — you're already 20% into your protein goal.</span></div>
      <div class="msg-user"><span>How am I doing overall?</span></div>
      <div class="energy-card">
        <div class="e-label">ENERGY SCORE</div>
        <div class="e-score">84</div>
        <div class="e-sub">Optimal · HRV up 12ms from yesterday</div>
        <div class="macro"><div class="macro-lbl">Protein</div><div class="macro-track"><div class="macro-fill" style="width:65%;background:#30D158"></div></div><div class="macro-val">104g</div></div>
        <div class="macro"><div class="macro-lbl">Carbs</div><div class="macro-track"><div class="macro-fill" style="width:40%;background:#FF9F0A"></div></div><div class="macro-val">12g</div></div>
        <div class="macro"><div class="macro-lbl">Fat</div><div class="macro-track"><div class="macro-fill" style="width:50%;background:#FF453A"></div></div><div class="macro-val">80g</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Features -->
<section class="section" id="features">
  <div class="label fade">What's inside</div>
  <h2 class="title fade">One app.<br>Actually everything.</h2>
  <p class="sub fade">Solas replaces your calorie tracker, workout log, wearable companion, macro calculator, and habit tracker — with a single conversation.</p>
  <div class="feat-grid fade">
    <div class="feat">
      <div class="feat-icon" style="background:rgba(10,132,255,0.12)">💬</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Natural language logging</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">Say what you ate, how you moved, how you slept. Solas parses it, logs it, and updates everything automatically. No forms. No dropdowns.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <div class="feat-icon" style="background:rgba(191,90,242,0.12)">🧠</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Compounding memory</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">Solas builds a permanent picture of you — goals, preferences, patterns, history. It compounds over time into a coach that genuinely knows you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <div class="feat-icon" style="background:rgba(48,209,88,0.12)">⚡</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Energy Score</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">Nutrition, sleep, HRV, recovery, and activity — all synthesized into one daily number. A real signal you can act on, not a vanity metric.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <div class="feat-icon" style="background:rgba(255,159,10,0.12)">⌚</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Wearable integration</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">Apple Health, Garmin, Whoop, Oura, and Strava all connected. Your data flows in silently. Solas reads it and tells you what it means.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <div class="feat-icon" style="background:rgba(100,210,255,0.12)">🌅</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Morning briefings</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">Wake up to a personalized summary — yesterday's recap, today's targets, and what to focus on. Ready before your first coffee.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat">
      <div class="feat-icon" style="background:rgba(255,69,58,0.12)">🎯</div>
      <div class="feat-title">Goal accountability</div>
      <p class="feat-desc">Tell Solas what you want. It builds the plan, tracks your streaks, generates meal plans and grocery lists, and checks in when you drift.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Wearables -->
<div class="section-wide">
  <div class="section-wide-inner">
    <div class="label fade">Works with everything you already use</div>
    <h2 class="title fade">Your devices.<br>Connected.</h2>
    <p class="sub fade">Solas reads your wearable data automatically — no manual syncing, no copy-pasting numbers. It synthesizes everything into context your AI coach actually understands.</p>
    <div class="wearable-row fade">
      <div class="wearable-pill"><div class="wearable-dot" style="background:#FF2D55"></div><div><div class="wearable-name">Apple Health</div><div class="wearable-status">Steps · HRV · Sleep · Workouts</div></div></div>
      <div class="wearable-pill"><div class="wearable-dot" style="background:#007AFF"></div><div><div class="wearable-name">Garmin</div><div class="wearable-status">Body Battery · VO2 Max · HRV</div></div></div>
      <div class="wearable-pill"><div class="wearable-dot" style="background:#FF9500"></div><div><div class="wearable-name">Whoop</div><div class="wearable-status">Recovery · Strain · Sleep</div></div></div>
      <div class="wearable-pill"><div class="wearable-dot" style="background:#34C759"></div><div><div class="wearable-name">Oura Ring</div><div class="wearable-status">Readiness · Temperature · HRV</div></div></div>
      <div class="wearable-pill"><div class="wearable-dot" style="background:#FC4C02"></div><div><div class="wearable-name">Strava</div><div class="wearable-status">Runs · Rides · Activities</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- How it works -->
<section class="section" id="how">
  <div class="label fade">How it works</div>
  <h2 class="title fade">Talk. It remembers.<br>You improve.</h2>
  <div class="how-grid">
    <div class="steps fade">
      <div class="step"><div class="step-n">1</div><div><h3>Tell Solas about yourself</h3><p>Set your goals, dietary approach, and activity level in a 2-minute onboarding. No long forms — just a conversation.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-n">2</div><div><h3>Log anything in plain English</h3><p>"3 eggs and coffee" · "45 min run" · "slept 5 hours, felt rough" — Solas understands it all and handles the rest automatically.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-n">3</div><div><h3>Connect your devices</h3><p>Link Apple Health, Garmin, Whoop, or Oura. Your wearable data syncs silently — no manual entry, ever.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-n">4</div><div><h3>Ask anything, anytime</h3><p>"How's my sleep been this week?" · "What should I eat for dinner?" · "Am I on track?" Real answers based on your real data.</p></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="demo fade">
      <div class="demo-hdr">
        <div class="demo-av">S</div>
        <div><div class="demo-name">Solas</div><div class="demo-status">Always on · Always learning</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="msg-user"><span>Give me my morning briefing</span></div>
